'''beatification'''

#The act of [[beatify]]ing, or the state of being beatified; esp., in the [[R. C. Church]], the act or process of ascertaining and declaring that a deceased person is one of "the [[blessed]]," or has attained the second degree of [[sanctity]], &mdash; usually a stage in the process of [[canonization]].

